tent from the series. The Ecosystem Explorer is a collection of videos, games, and infographics designed to take students deep into the ecosystems of three thrilling animals: vultures, wolves, and sharks.\r\n\r\nRelated videos introduce each ecosystem and explore the relationship between animals and humans which is often more complicated than we realize. The microsite has been developed to encourage students to discover more about the ecology and conservation of these three worlds by exploring games, videos and infographics.\r\n\r\nBuilt using Create JS, Tilt showcased their advanced knowledge of HTML5 to take the project beyond the Flash requirements of the brief to an exciting new level. Tilt also developed dynamic illustrations for the games which were enhanced by suitably graphic sound effects!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.pbslearningmedia.org/resource/5aeed659-7f0b-417f-81d9-5f2e9c747644/ecosystem-explorer-earth-a-new-wild/\" target=\"_blank\">Experience it for yourself.</a>'),(566,128,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(567,128,'image_5','247'),(568,128,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(569,128,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(570,172,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/pbs_featured.jpg'),(571,172,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:960;s:6:\"height\";i:960;s:4:\"file\";s:24:\"2015/09/pbs_featured.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:24:\"pbs_featured-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:24:\"pbs_featured-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:24:\"pbs_featured-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"fo