get=\"_blank\">Mud Mile</a>, with the latter seeing our very own Stig Coldham fall head first into waist deep mud and emerge covered in more mud that Arnold Schwarzenegger in the end scene from Predator. Our very own \'ultimate frisbee\' warrior Miles Tincknell, pranced round the course with the speed, agility and grace of a gazelle, leaving Stig and Jon (10 years his senior) to pontificate on the joys of youth. \r\n\r\nSee you in 2016 Tough Mudder. Anyone up for a challenge? '),(626,104,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(627,104,'image_5',''),(628,104,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(629,104,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(630,175,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/tm_header.jpg'),(631,175,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1280;s:6:\"height\";i:540;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2015/09/tm_header.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"tm_header-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"tm_header-300x127.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:127;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"tm_header-1024x432.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:432;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"tm_header-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(632,175,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Tough Mudder'),(633,176,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/tm_featured.jpg'),(634,176,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:960;s:6:\"height\";i:960;s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"2015/09/tm_featured.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\