sheer breadth of diverse projects we work on. Our eclectic skillset and innovative design approach means that every day there is an explosion of creative anarchy within our four walls. But how do you bring this to life?'),(881,98,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(882,98,'image_1','231'),(883,98,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(884,98,'image_2','232'),(885,98,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(886,98,'image_3','233'),(887,98,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(888,98,'image_4','266'),(889,98,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(890,98,'main_body_of_text','During the development an animated masthead for our new website, we carried out a series of experimental test shoots to try to encapsulate the Tilt brand. We eschewed any CGI trickery to develop a series of liquid artworks to reflect the kaleidoscopic blend of creative elements coming together to deliver truly unique results. Mixing inks in water, and using different surface tension, we created a captivating series of images with colourful flow and movement.\r\n\r\nWhen searching for an audio track to support the piece we thought of Ninja Tune, an independent record label based in London. They put us in touch with Submotion Orchestra who were looking for a video for their latest EP.  Submotion Orchestra make some of the most interesting and exciting music from the UK today: A kaleidoscope of electronic bass music and entrancing vocals. We all agreed that our video would provide the perfect backdrop to their highly atmospheric music, which is at once delicate and heavy, spacious and dense, highly atmospheric but firmly rooted. Our video complements their music perfectly and were proud to collaborate with true musical pioneers.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container--newsvideo\">\r\n    <div class=\"group-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"module module--16-9 module--video module--nozoom\">\r\n            <div class=\"ratio\">\r\n                <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/138964426\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\niTunes - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III-it\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III-it</a>\r\nNinjashop - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III</a>'),(891,98,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(892,98,'image_5','235'),(893,98,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(894,98,'_','field_5629e968f9254'),(895,198,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/learning_header.jpg'),(896,198,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1280;s:6:\"height\";i:540;s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"2015/09/learning_header.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"learning_header-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"learning_header-300x127.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:127;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"learning_header-1024x432.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:432;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"learning_header-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(897,198,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Learning'),(898,199,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/learning_featured.jpg'),(899,199,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:960;s:6:\"height\";i:960;s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"2015/09/learning_featured.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"learning_featured-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\"