y really muddy! Whats not to like?\r\n\r\nThe course took a little over 3 hours, with some great new obstacles introduced by the Tough Mudder team. Our favorites were <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/obstacles/king-swingers\" target=\"_blank\">King of the Swingers</a> and  <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/content/mud-mile-20\" target=\"_blank\">Mud Mile</a>, with the latter seeing our very own Stig Coldham fall head first into waist deep mud and emerge covered in more mud that Arnold Schwarzenegger in the end scene from Predator. \r\n\r\nSee you in 2016 Tough Mudder. Anyone up for a challenge?'),(1284,228,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(1285,228,'image_5',''),(1286,228,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(1287,228,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(1290,229,'header_image','175'),(1291,229,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(1292,229,'intro_text','Throughout the course of the year select members of the Tilt team have been battling the elements in an attempt to build up the stamina required to face the Tough Mudder challenge. '),(1293,229,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(1294,229,'image_1','224'),(1295,229,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(1296,229,'image_2','225'),(1297,229,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(1298,229,'image_3','226'),(1299,229,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(1300,229,'image_4','227'),(1301,229,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(1302,229,'main_body_of_text','Tough Mudder is a team-oriented 10-12 mile (18-20 km) obstacle course designed to test physical strength and mental grit. Putting Camaraderie over finisher rankings this event allows participants to experience world class obstacles. Well this is what the events site said, but to be perfectly honest with you, we all just fancied the chance to get really really muddy! Whats not to like? Check out our <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/130366057\" target=\"_blank\">training video</a> . . . if you can call it training!\r\n\r\nThe course took a little over 3 hours, with some great new obstacles introduced by the Tough Mudder team. Our favorites were <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/obstacles/king-swingers\" target=\"_blank\">King of the Swingers</a> and  <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/content/mud-mile-20\" target=\"_blank\">Mud Mile</a>, with the latter seeing our very own Stig Coldham fall head first into waist deep mud and emerge covered in more mud that Arnold Schwarzenegger in the end scene from Predator. \r\n\r\nSee you in 2016 Tough Mudder. Anyone up for a challenge?'),(1303,229,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(1304,229,'image_5',''),(1305,229,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(1306,229,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(1309,230,'header_image','194'),(1310,230,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(1311,230,'intro_text','We sometimes find it a bit tricky to describe Tilt in a way that reflects the wide range of creative services and the sheer breadth of diverse projects we work on. Our eclectic skillset and innovative design approach means that every day there is an explosion of creative anarchy within our four walls. But how do you bring this to life?'),(1312,230,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(1313,230,'image_1',''),(1314,230,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(1315,230,'image_2',''),(1316,230,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(1317,230,'image_3',''),(1318,230,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(1319,230,'image_4',''),(1320,230,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(1321,230,'main_body_of_text','During the development an animated masthead for our new website, we carried out a series of experimental test shoots to try to encapsulate the Tilt brand. We eschewed any CGI trickery to develop a series of liquid artworks to reflect the kaleidoscopic blend of creative elements coming together to deliver truly unique results. Mixing inks in water, and using different surface tension, we created a captivating series of images with colourful flow and movement.\r\n\r\nWhen searching for an audio track to support the piece we thought of Ninja Tune, an independent record label based in London. They put us in touch with Submotion Orchestra who were looking for a video for their latest EP.  Submotion Orchestra make some of the most interesting and exciting music from the UK today: A kaleidoscope of electronic bass music and entrancing vocals. We all agreed that our video would provide the perfect backdrop to their highly atmospheric music, which is at once delicate and heavy, spacious and dense, highly atmospheric but firmly rooted. Our video complements their music perfectly and were proud to collaborate with true musical pioneers.\r\n\r\nThe release - EP III, can be found on:\r\n\r\niTunes - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III-it\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III-it</a>\r\nNinjashop - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III</a>'),(1322,230,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(1323,230,'image_5',''),(1324,230,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(1325,230,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(1326,98,'_wp_old_slug','post-14'),(1327,231,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/sub_lg_one_v2.jpg'),(1328,231,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:960;s:6:\"height\";i:960;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2015/09/sub_lg_one_v2.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"sub_lg_one_v2-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"sub_lg_one_v2-300x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"sub_lg_one_v2-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(1