ng across film, design, motion and development, experience of integration will be experienced first hand. If you are interested then send your CV to recruitment@wearetilt.com with the subject line \'Motion intern\'.'),(2580,330,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(2581,330,'image_5',''),(2582,330,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(2583,330,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(2586,331,'header_image','325'),(2587,331,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(2588,331,'intro_text','Are you a talented motion graphics freelancer looking for work? We would love to meet you and discuss your showreel over a cuppa! '),(2589,331,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(2590,331,'image_1','309'),(2591,331,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(2592,331,'image_2','293'),(2593,331,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(2594,331,'image_3','300'),(2595,331,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(2596,331,'image_4','303'),(2597,331,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(2598,331,'main_body_of_text','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.'),(2599,331,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(2600,331,'image_5',''),(2601,331,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(2602,331,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(2603,332,'_wp_attached_file','2015/10/jobs_mh_02_hz.jpg'),(2604,332,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1200;s:6:\"height\";i:605;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2015/10/jobs_mh_02_hz.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"jobs_mh_02_hz-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"jobs_mh_02_hz-300x151.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:151;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"jobs_mh_02_hz-1024x516.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:516;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"jobs_mh_02_hz-825x510.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:825;s:6:\"height\";i:510;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:11:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";i:0;}}'),(2605,332,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Careers'),(2608,333,'header_image','332'),(2609,333,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(2610,333,'intro_text','We are looking for a talented Interactive Designer with a proven track record in producing breath taking digital content. Youll be working closely with the Creative Director and the rest of the design department to produce websites, applications, interactive content, social media campaigns and branding for a wide range of clients from multi-national organisations to charities. Were a busy agency so youll be comfortable working to tight deadlines in a busy environment.'),(2611,333,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(2612,333,'image_1','293'),(2613,333,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(2614,333,'image_2','294'),(2615,333,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(2616,333,'image_3','295'),(2617,333,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(2618,333,'image_4','297'),(2619,333,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(2620,333,'main_body_of_text','As well as being an ace designer youll be able to discuss creative concepts and be comfortable throwing around ideas  everyone gets involved here.\r\n\r\nYoull also be working closely with our dev team, turning your static designs into working browser based pages for multiple platforms. So although you wont be coding yourself, an excellent knowledge of whats possible and an active interest in the ever changing digital landscape is a must.\r\n\r\nWhile your focus will be on our creative output, were a small team so youll be involved in all the other stuff that goes with working in an agency  supporting the senior team, liaising with clients, managing your time, tea rounds and generally helping out. So your creativity should be matched by a good level of organisation, a can do attitude and a willingness to muck in.\r\n\r\nExcellent knowledge of using Adobe Fireworks, Illustrator, Photoshop and InDesign, etc\r\n\r\n Knowledge of developing cross-browser and cross-platform compatible solutions\r\n A good knowledge of current trends, techniques and best practices\r\n An active interest in emerging technologies\r\n A keen interest in social media and its impact\r\n A good understanding of user experience and wireframe design\r\n Knowledge of SEO and web accessibility\r\n Speed, accuracy and excellent attention to detail\r\n A keen interest in typography\r\n Excellent communication skills\r\n Comfortable with using a Mac\r\n Ability to use your initiative and work well under pressure to achieve tight deadlines\r\n A flexible attitude with proven experience of working in a small team\r\n A positive outlook, good sense of humour and lack of pretence\r\n A love of tea and good music\r\n Dont mind dogs  we have one in the office\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in applying for this position then please send you CV and examples of your work to <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@wearetilt.com\">recruitment@wearetilt.com</a> along with a supporting letter stating why you think you would be right for the role.\r\n\r\nPlease indicate your salary expectations in your response.'),(2621,333,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(2622,333,'image_5',''),(2623,333,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(2624,333,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(2641,340,'header_image','194'),(2642,340,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(2643,340,'intro_text','We sometimes find it a bit tricky to describe Tilt in a way that reflects the wide range of creative services and the sheer breadth of diverse projects we work on. Our eclectic skillset and innovative design approach means that every day there is an explosion of creative anarchy within our four walls. But how do you bring this to life?'),(2644,340,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(2645,340,'image_1','231'),(2646,340,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(2647,340,'image_2','232'),(2648,340,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(2649,340,'image_3','233'),(2650,340,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(2651,340,'image_4','266'),(2652,340,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(2653,340,'main_body_of_text','During the development an animated masthead for our new website, we carried out a series of experimental test shoots to try to encapsulate the Tilt brand. We eschewed any CGI trickery to develop a series of liquid artworks to reflect the kaleidoscopic blend of creative elements coming together to deliver truly unique results. Mixing inks in water, and using different surface tension, we created a captivating series of images with colourful flow and movement.\r\n\r\nWhen searching for an audio track to support the piece we thought of Ninja Tune, an independent record label based in London. They put us in touch with Submotion Orchestra who were looking for a video for their latest EP.  Submotion Orchestra make some of the most interesting and exciting music from the UK today: A kaleidoscope of electronic bass music and entrancing vocals. We all agreed that our video would provide the perfect backdrop to their highly atmospheric music, which is at once delicate and heavy, spacious and dense, highly atmospheric but firmly rooted. Our video complements their music perfectly and were proud to collaborate with true musical pioneers.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container--newsvideo\">\r\n    <div class=\"group-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"module module--16-9 module--video module--nozoom\">\r\n            <div class=\"ratio\">\r\n                <iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/138964426\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe> \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\niTunes - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III-it\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III-it</a>\r\nNinjashop - <a href=\"http://found.ee/III\" target=\"_blank\">http://found.ee/III</a>'),(2654,340,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(2655,340,'image_5','235'),(2656,340,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(2657,340,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(2660,341,'header_image','175'),(2661,341,'_header_image','field_560bb9af7ac4d'),(2662,341,'intro_text','Throughout the course of the year select members of the Tilt team have been battling the elements in an attempt to build up the stamina required to face the Tough Mudder challenge. '),(2663,341,'_intro_text','field_560ba1b2a1f36'),(2664,341,'image_1','224'),(2665,341,'_image_1','field_560ba235a1f37'),(2666,341,'image_2','225'),(2667,341,'_image_2','field_560ba25da1f38'),(2668,341,'image_3','226'),(2669,341,'_image_3','field_560ba272a1f39'),(2670,341,'image_4','227'),(2671,341,'_image_4','field_560ba279a1f3a'),(2672,341,'main_body_of_text','Tough Mudder is a team-oriented 10-12 mile (18-20 km) obstacle course designed to test physical strength and mental grit. Putting Camaraderie over finisher rankings this event allows participants to experience world class obstacles. Well this is what the events site said, but to be perfectly honest with you, we all just fancied the chance to get really really muddy! Whats not to like? \r\n\r\n<div class=\"container--newsvideo\">\r\n    <div class=\"group-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"module module--16-9 module--video module--nozoom\">\r\n            <div class=\"ratio\">\r\n<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/130366057?title=0&byline=0&portrait=0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nThe course took a little over 3 hours, with some great new obstacles introduced by the Tough Mudder team. Our favorites were <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/obstacles/king-swingers\" target=\"_blank\">King of the Swingers</a> and  <a href=\"https://toughmudder.co.uk/content/mud-mile-20\" target=\"_blank\">Mud Mile</a>, with the latter seeing our very own Stig Coldham fall head first into waist deep mud and emerge covered in more mud that Arnold Schwarzenegger in the end scene from Predator. Our very own \'ultimate frisbee\' warrior Miles Tincknell, pranced round the course with the speed, agility and grace of a gazelle, leaving Stig and Jon (10 years his senior) to pontificate on the joys of youth. \r\n\r\nSee you in 2016 Tough Mudder. Anyone up for a challenge? '),(2673,341,'_main_body_of_text','field_560ba292a1f3b'),(2674,341,'image_5',''),(2675,341,'_image_5','field_560ba32ea1f3c'),(2676,341,'_','field_560bb9ca7ac4e'),(2677,342,'_wp_attached_file','2015/09/bdf_md_one.jpg'),(2678,342,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:480;s:6:\"height\";i:480;s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"2015/09/bdf_md_one.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"bdf_md_one-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"bdf_md_one-300x300.jpg\";s: